Usage: get_pg_nets [-help] [-filter <expr>] [ -of_objects <object_list>]

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-filter <expr>                     # Filters the collection with the specified
                                   # expression (string, optional)
-of_objects <object_list>          # Creates a collection of all PG nets
                                   # associated with the specified cells or pg
                                   # pins (string, optional)